Title: Radio Delta FM 101.7
Description: رادیو دلتا لبنان Radio Delta is a distinguished Arabic radio station that broadcasts from Lebanon and covers Syria, Cyprus and Jordan. Due to its huge success and its high listenership, it’s been selected number 1 for more than 3 consecutive years. Today Radio Delta takes itself to a whole new level with the revamp of its shows targeting a more youthful audience and the broadcast of the latest Arabic and English hits to please all your tastes.  You can listen to Radio Delta on 101.7, 101.9 FM. You can find us online www.radiodelta.fm: listen to the station wherever you are in the world, check our latest programs, listen to our exclusive songs & follow up on the latest stars news. You can also find us on mobile applications (Blackberry, iPhone and Androide).  Radio Delta covers a wide range of programs: educational, sport news, entertainment, music news, local & international events, interviews and live coverage. Stay connected, stay updated and most importantly stay tuned!
